&lt;li&gt;Plan and execute experiments, maintain an accurate record of experimental details, in-depth data analysis, and clear communication of these results through documentation and presentations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Write protocols, develop procedures, and maintain accurate records.&lt;/li&gt;
