&lt;li&gt;Strong collaboration and communication skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Desire to be part of a rapidly evolving organization, with a compelling technology, and taking products and processes to the next level.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
