&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;10x Genomics makes products that enable researchers to answer biology&#39;s hardest and most elusive questions. Our web experience is how the global research community discovers our products, evaluates them, and ultimately buys, and we are seeking a Senior Product Manager to lead the continuous evolution of that experience end-to-end.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role is built for a product leader who blends strong web product craft and UX judgment with the technical fluency to shape how our site captures, structures, and hands off customer data to the systems behind it. You will partner closely with engineering and commercial leaders to launch intuitive, self-service web solutions that delight users and drive pipeline. You will also shape how the web platform connects into marketing automation platforms, CRM, CDPs, and the broader stack so that web behavior translates cleanly into qualified demand.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You&#39;ll Be Doing&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
