&lt;li&gt;Experience working with challenging clinical sample types (e.g., FFPE tissue, primary tumor cells, low-input samples).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working within a quality system or environment governed by CLIA, CAP, or ISO 13485 standards strongly preferred.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prior hands-on experience with 10x Genomics single-cell or spatial technologies (e.g., Chromium or Xenium platforms)

