&lt;p&gt;We are looking for an outstanding individual to join our Program Management group as part of the &lt;strong&gt;10X R&amp;amp;D team in Pleasanton&lt;/strong&gt;.&amp;nbsp; You will work on Program teams with biologists, chemists, engineers, computational biologists, and software engineers who are developing truly new products. Our products have allowed researchers to study biology at unprecedented resolution and scale; yielding insights in diverse fields such as cancer biology, immunology, neuroscience, and developmental biology.&lt;/p&gt;
